123
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,070
That's all right.

124
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,550
Magistrate, do you know?

125
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,600
20 years ago,

126
00:08:30,110 --> 00:08:31,600
when I was in the capital,

127
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:35,040
