hoping for eternity.

139
00:09:04,110 --> 00:09:05,440
Since my father passed away,

140
00:09:06,070 --> 00:09:08,160
this poem has always been with me.

141
00:09:09,070 --> 00:09:10,510
It's my good fortune

142
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,350
to meet his old friend today.

143
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:14,510
But

144
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,390
