148
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,200
Yes.

149
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,550
Yinlian changed me.

150
00:09:28,230 --> 00:09:29,920
Ever since I married her,

151
00:09:30,950 --> 00:09:33,000
