155
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,950
who indulges himself in her charm

156
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:45,270
and writes love letters.

157
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,790
Now that I'm over 50,

158
00:09:49,070 --> 00:09:50,510
