00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,520
Fresh soil.

589
00:33:20,470 --> 00:33:22,190
If I want to dig up the grave
and check the body,

590
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:24,280
Mr. Chen,

591
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:25,950
can you do me a favor?

592
00:33:28,950 --> 00:33:29,430
Magistrate,

593
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,470
I'm afraid that's against the rules.

594
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:36,470
Yes.

595
00:33:37,830 --> 00:33:38,830
I've gone beyond my authority.

596
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,560
I have a list of prisoners in my room.

597
00:33:41,710 --> 00:33:42,880
If you don't believe me,

598
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:44,070
you can check it.

599
00:33:44,800 --> 00:33:45,590
That won't be necessary.

600
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:48,880
Since I'm here and I've seen it,

601
00:33:48,950 --> 00:33:49,710
I've

602
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,160
done my job.

603
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:57,880
I appreciate your understanding.

604
00:33:59,000 --> 00:33:59,470
Let's go.

605
00:34:01,950 --> 00:34:02,430
Thank you very much.

606
00:34:14,160 --> 00:34:14,800
Magistrate,

607
00:34:15,560 --> 00:34:16,880
what do we do now?

608
00:34:27,160 --> 00:34:27,800
Magistrate.

609
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:29,040
Dig the grave.

610
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:30,310
Dig the grave?

611
00:34:31,470 --> 00:34:32,950
The quarry is heavily guarded.

612
00:34:33,160 --> 00:34:34,470
It's hard to get in again.

613
00:34:34,950 --> 00:34:35,470
Let's wait.

614
00:34:36,110 --> 00:34:36,760
In a while,

615
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:39,470
someone should be here to show us the way.

616
00:34:43,640 --> 00:34:44,430
Magistrate.

617
00:34:49,160 --> 00:34:49,640
Magistrate,

618
00:34:50,190 --> 00:34:51,000
you know Bazong?

619
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,640
He's a friend of mine.

620
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:54,830
If that's the case,

621
00:34:54,830 --> 00:34:56,520
it's not a waste for me to risk my life.

622
00:34:56,640 --> 00:34:57,070
Magistrate,

623
00:34:57,190 --> 00:34:58,710
you want to dig up the grave
and check the body?

624
00:34:59,190 --> 00:34:59,560
Yes.

625
00:35:00,830 --> 00:35:01,950
There's a path ahead

626
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:03,760
that leads to the mass grave.

627
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:04,350
Please

628
00:35:04,350 --> 00:35:05,070
follow me.

629
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:06,560
Please.

630
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:21,560
Magistrate.

631
00:35:22,190 --> 00:35:22,680
Dig.

632
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:37,230
Magistrate,

633
00:35:37,950 --> 00:35:38,710
this place is heavily guarded.

634
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:39,560
If he didn't die of illness,

635
00:35:39,590 --> 00:35:41,230
then Mr. Chen must have let him go.

636
00:35:41,230 --> 00:35:42,000
This kind of thing

637
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:42,590
happens all the time.

638
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:43,920
I'm a petty man.

639
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:44,590
I don't know much about it.

640
00:35:44,830 --> 00:35:45,160
Magistrate,

641
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,590
that's all I can do for you.

642
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:50,000
You're willing to take such a risk.

643
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:52,040
Is it to help me

644
00:35:52,430 --> 00:35:53,430
or for Bazong?

645
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:55,630
Bazong helped my family a lot.

646
00:35:55,710 --> 00:35:56,320
I should return the favor.

647
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:57,230
It's the right thing to do.

648
00:35:57,560 --> 00:35:58,950
If you're a friend of the Bazong,

649
00:35:58,950 --> 00:35:59,710
helping you

650
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,390
means helping the Bazong.

651
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:03,560
Thank you very much.

652
00:36:04,190 --> 00:36:05,040
You're very welcome.

653
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:11,600
Magistrate.

654
00:36:33,390 --> 00:36:34,280
Don't yell.

655
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:36,950
Let him look at the straw mat.

656
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:41,360
Is that Li Han?

657
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,360
I'll ask you again.

658
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:46,800
Where is Li Han?

659
00:36:47,430 --> 00:36:49,000
You have no right to ask me.

660
00:36:49,950 --> 00:36:51,950
The provincial governor's letter
doesn't work for you?

661
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:53,520
Do you have it?

662
00:36:53,910 --> 00:36:54,430
I don't.

663
00:36:57,800 --> 00:36:59,430
Then you're faking an official document.

664
00:36:59,950 --> 00:37:01,670
You're faking... an official document...

665
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:05,600
If you don't tell the truth,

666
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:08,840
I'll kill you now.

667
00:37:09,670 --> 00:37:11,710
I can not only judge

668
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:13,560
but also decide cases.

669
00:37:14,430 --> 00:37:15,710
Maybe, in the end,

670
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:18,320
your case will fall into my hands.

671
00:37:18,910 --> 00:37:21,950
I'll make sure you'll die for nothing.

672
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:24,520
Are you on earth

673
00:37:24,910 --> 00:37:26,520
an official or a villain?

674
00:37:27,430 --> 00:37:29,120
When I meet an official, I'm an official.

675
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,800
When I meet a villain,
I'll kill a villain.